{block title}iPub:Websockets! extension{/block}

{block content}
    <div class="uk-grid" data-uk-grid-margin>
        <div class="uk-width-medium-1-1">

            <div class="uk-vertical-align uk-text-center" style="background: url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,') 50% 0 no-repeat; height: 450px;">
                <div class="uk-vertical-align-middle uk-width-1-2">
                    <h1 class="uk-heading-large">iPublikuj:websockets!</h1>
                    <p class="uk-text-large">Websockets implementation into Nette framework.</p>
                    <p>
                        <a href="https://github.com/iPublikuj/websockets" class="uk-button uk-button-large"><i class="uk-icon-github"></i> Github</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <hr />

    <div class="uk-grid" data-uk-grid-margin>
        <div class="uk-width-medium-1-3">
            <div class="uk-grid">
                <div class="uk-width-1-6">
                    <i class="uk-icon-bolt uk-icon-large uk-text-primary"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="uk-width-5-6">
                    <h2 class="uk-h3">Fast & Easy</h2>

                    <p>It's super easy to create web sockets application like your own chat or system messaging</p>

                    <p>After understanding "the new flow" - event driven programming, compared to traditional HTTP request/response - writing any application with this extensions & Nette framework becomes fast and easy.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="uk-width-medium-1-3">
            <div class="uk-grid">
                <div class="uk-width-1-6">
                    <i class="uk-icon-bicycle uk-icon-large uk-text-primary"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="uk-width-5-6">
                    <h2 class="uk-h3">Routes & Controllers</h2>

                    <p>Routes will help you implement application endpoint. You could create eg. chat route and notification route with separated parameters etc.</p>

                    <p>Controllers are connected with routes and like in classic Nette application, each route represent one controller.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="uk-width-medium-1-3">
            <div class="uk-grid">
                <div class="uk-width-1-6">
                    <i class="uk-icon-thumbs-o-up uk-icon-large uk-text-primary"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="uk-width-5-6">
                    <h2 class="uk-h3">Nette compatible</h2>

                    <p>This collection of extensions is fully compatible with latest Nette framework</p>

                    <p>All extensions are respecting all Nette desing patterns.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr />

    <h1>Demo application</h1>

    <div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box uk-margin-bottom" id="join-box">
        <form name="join" class="uk-form uk-grid">

            <div class="uk-width-6-10 uk-container-center uk-margin-top uk-margin-bottom">
                <div class="uk-grid uk-grid-small">
                    <div class="uk-width-6-10">
                        <input name="nick" type="text" class="uk-width-1-1 uk-form-large" placeholder="Type your name" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="uk-width-4-10">
                        <button name="join" class="uk-width-1-1 uk-button uk-button-large"><i class="uk-icon-plug"></i> Join</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </form>
    </div>

    <div class="uk-grid uk-grid-small uk-margin-bottom uk-hidden" id="chat-box">
        <div class="uk-width-3-10 rooms">
            <div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box">
                <h3 class="uk-panel-title">Select room</h3>
                <ul class="uk-nav uk-nav-side">
                    <li class="uk-clearfix">
                        <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="uk-float-right uk-hidden leave-room" title="Leave room" data-uk-tooltip><i class="uk-icon-sign-out"></i></a>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="room" data-room-id="general" data-room-topic="/demo-chat/general">General</a>
                        <ul class="uk-nav-sub"></ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="uk-width-7-10">
            <div class="messages uk-panel uk-panel-box uk-panel-box-secondary uk-width-1-1 uk-margin-small-bottom">

            </div>

            <form name="new-message" class="uk-form uk-grid uk-grid-small uk-hidden">
                <div class="uk-width-6-10">
                    <input name="message" disabled="disabled" type="text" class="uk-width-1-1" placeholder="Type here...">
                </div>
                <div class="uk-width-2-10">
                    <button name="send" disabled="disabled" class="uk-button uk-width-1-1"><i class="uk-icon-send"></i> Send</button>
                </div>
                <div class="uk-width-2-10">
                    <a n:href="advert!" class="advert ajax uk-button uk-button-primary uk-width-1-1 uk-disabled"><i class="uk-icon-gift"></i> Advert</a>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
{/block}

{block #scripts}
    {include #parent}
    <script src="/components/jquery-timeago/jquery.timeago.js"></script>
    <script src="/components/ipub-websockets-wamp/public/js/autobahn.js"></script>
    <script src="/components/ipub-websockets-wamp/public/js/ipub.websockets.wamp.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/chat.js"></script>
{/block}
